REVIEW
OF
THE
PITOT
TUBE
THIS
PAPER
IS
AN
ATTEMPT
TO
BRING
TOGETHER
THE
IMPORTANT
INFORMATION
REGARDING
PITOT
TUBES
AND
THEIR
USE
TO
SUMMARIZE
THE
AVAILABLE
DATA
ON
THE
APPLICATION
OF
VARIOUS
TYPES
OF
IMPACT
AND
VELOCITY
PROBES
FOR
THE
GUIDANCE
OF
ENGINEERS
AND
RESEARCH
WORKERS
AND
TO
AID
THEM
IN
THE
DESIGN
OF
FLOW
INSTRUMENTS
FOR
SPECIFIC
APPLICATIONS
